31:49.282 --> 31:52.327
Right. She's out a lot.

31:53.202 --> 31:55.163
Well, what do you love to do?

31:55.246 --> 31:58.249
What's your dream?
I wanna know what your dream is.

32:01.711 --> 32:02.712
Um…

32:04.505 --> 32:06.758
