34:08.796 --> 34:10.798
I'm like a big Bruce Fulper fan.

34:10.882 --> 34:14.218
I heard they were playin',
and I was like, "Fuck it, I'll hitchhike."

34:16.512 --> 34:17.346
Cool.

34:18.306 --> 34:20.016
What time you gotta be there?

34:20.099 --> 34:21.392
Show's at 7:30.

34:33.237 --> 34:34.363
How about this?

34:35.156 --> 34:37.867
I was just headed home
to crack open a few brewskis.

34:39.535 --> 34:40.995
How about you come with me?

34:41.996 --> 34:45.208
I got some weed. And drink a few beers.

34:46.667 --> 34:47.877
Lift some weights.

34:50.421 --> 34:53.174
And then, uh, I'll drive you out there.

34:54.592 --> 34:56.260
Yeah, man, that sounds great.

35:04.018 --> 35:04.977
What's your name?

35:06.854 --> 35:07.855
Jeff.

35:08.356 --> 35:09.690
Nice to meet you, Jeff.

35:10.399 --> 35:11.818
