into working out all of a sudden.

35:31.921 --> 35:34.966
You know, suddenly,
uh, everybody's jogging.

35:35.466 --> 35:38.136
That ain't gonna cut it
for skinny guys like us, you know?

35:39.595 --> 35:41.722
We gotta lift weights.

35:41.806 --> 35:44.433
Or, like,
chicks ain't even gonna notice us.

35:45.184 --> 35:47.311
-Yeah, exactly.
-That's right.

35:48.646 --> 35:49.856
Jeez.

35:51.524 --> 35:53.693
One more. One more. Yeah. Come on.

35:58.447 --> 36:00.241
Yeah. Nice.

36:00.950 --> 36:03.369
You are fuckin' strong, man.

36:04.662 --> 36:06.956
Yeah, well, I've been workin' out a lot.

36:07.039 --> 36:07.957
I could tell.

36:09.917 --> 36:12.420
-You try it, dude. I'll spot you.
-No. No, no.

36:12.503 --> 36:14.255
-Come on.
-I'm all right. I'm all right.

36:14.338 --> 36:16.549
I… What time is it?

36:18.050 --> 36:19.844
I feel like we should get movin'.

36:22.054 --> 36:24.223
