36:25.308 --> 36:27.435
You want another beer?
We'll have one more beer.

36:27.518 --> 36:28.728
I just…

36:29.312 --> 36:31.063
I'm meeting my buddies there
at, like, seven.

36:31.147 --> 36:32.523
