maybe we could have it on the way.

36:50.291 --> 36:52.251
I just don't want
to miss the concert, you know.

36:52.335 --> 36:54.378
Like, it's Pegasus, man!

36:57.715 --> 36:59.467
You worry too much, jeez.

37:09.518 --> 37:10.603
What the f--?

37:13.564 --> 37:15.191
-What?
-What the--? I mean…

37:16.317 --> 37:17.735
-What?
-Why'd you do that?

37:19.445 --> 37:20.947
I was just joking.

37:21.030 --> 37:22.615
'Cause I'm not that way, man.

37:22.698 --> 37:26.869
Neither am I.
I was just jokin' around. Just sit down.

37:26.953 --> 37:29.205
