38:03.864 --> 38:05.241
Are you fucking crying?

38:06.617 --> 38:08.911
-No.
-What the fuck? Jesus.

38:08.995 --> 38:10.997
I'm… I'm outta here, man.

38:11.497 --> 38:13.374
